metadata.name: Divine Blaque Angel Genesis
metadata.description: "She who watches over all divine beings" - The Divine Blaque Angel is an archetype or energy that any being can embody. She is the inspiration to become what it is you desire to become, to create what it is you desire to create. She represents the love that exists within all our creations. She is the dreamer, the creator, the scientist, the illusionist, the genius, the God.
